# Delta Watcher Module v1.0
## Role
Track and compare changes across time, sensors, and layers.
## Inputs
- multi-sensory data streams
- temporal sequences
- contextual states
## Functions
1. Within-Sense Tracking
   - detect local changes (Δx)
2. Cross-Sense Comparison
   - compare Δx across channels
3. Consistency Filtering
   - retain signals that persist across sensors
4. Contradiction Detection
   - flag mismatches (hidden structure)
5. Temporal Smoothing
   - ignore noise, track persistent trends
## Output
- stable signals
- anomaly alerts
- pattern emergence
## Core Principle
Truth persists across independent measurements over time.

